<HEAD>Pell `Out Of It,' Says Schneider</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CRANSTON, R.I. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   <LOCATION>U.S.</LOCATION> Rep. <PERSON>Claudine Schneider</PERSON> says voters
regard 71-year-old <PERSON>Sen. Claiborne Pell</PERSON> as being ``out of it.''
   Pell's campaign manager said <PERSON>Miss Schneider</PERSON> was becoming
``desperate'' in her campaign against the senator, who is ahead in
the polls.
   ``She sees him daily,'' said <PERSON>Mary Beth Cahill</PERSON>. ``She knows
that's not true.''
